<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank you for contacting me</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #10b981;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #10b981;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #64748b;
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .message p {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .message p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .subject-reference {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #2563eb;
        }
        .cta-button.secondary {
            background-color: #6b7280;
        }
        .cta-button.secondary:hover {
            background-color: #4b5563;
        }
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .social-links h3 {
            color: #374151;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .social-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .signature {
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .signature p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ú® Thank You for Reaching Out!</h1>
            <p>Your message has been received successfully</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hi {{name}},
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                <p>Thank you for taking the time to contact me through my portfolio website! üéâ</p>
                
                <p>I have successfully received your message and truly appreciate your interest in my work. Your inquiry is important to me, and I'm excited to connect with you.</p>
                
                <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
                <p>I will personally review your message and get back to you as soon as possible, typically within 24-48 hours. I believe in providing thoughtful and detailed responses, so please bear with me as I craft a proper reply.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="subject-reference">
                <strong>Your message subject:</strong> "{{subject}}"
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{portfolioUrl}}" class="cta-button">
                    üåê Explore My Portfolio
                </a>
                <a href="{{portfolioUrl}}#projects" class="cta-button secondary">
                    üíº View My Projects
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="social-links">
                <h3>ü§ù Let's Connect</h3>
                <p>While you wait for my response, feel free to connect with me on social media:</p>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/prince-kumar" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/prince-kumar" class="social-link">GitHub</a>
                <a href="{{portfolioUrl}}" class="social-link">Portfolio</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="signature">
            <h3>{{ownerName}}</h3>
            <p>Full-Stack Developer</p>
            <p>Building innovative web solutions</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>üìß This is an automated response.</strong> Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>If you need immediate assistance, you can reach me directly at <a href="mailto:{{ownerEmail}}" style="color: #3b82f6;">{{ownerEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>Visit my <a href="{{portfolioUrl}}" style="color: #3b82f6;">portfolio website</a> for more information about my work.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>